description:
Texas Senator Ted Cruz calls in to talk about the flood of unvaccinated and maskless illegal aliens pouring across the southern border. General Milley needs to answer before a committee. Biden's unconstitutional vaccine mandate is to distract from his many failures. A very interesting statistic out of the state of Florida. Biden tries to turn country against republican governors. Callers share their vaccination thoughts.
